Vibrational entropy               ...      0.00808695 Eh      5.07 kcal/mol
Rotational entropy                ...      0.01273909 Eh      7.99 kcal/mol
Translational entropy             ...      0.01864317 Eh     11.70 kcal/mol
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Final entropy term                ...      0.04012366 Eh     25.18 kcal/mol

